YAML-Yaml2Html version 0.01
===========================

This uses the YAML parser to convert a specialized YAML document
into an HTML page.  This module is Pure Perl, and requires no
c compiler, etc etc.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    YAML

